"Birenzeho OYA Impuzandengo -  Ubwiza ) Hanyuma Buhoro , A Porogaramu-shoboza "
"Gicurasi iminsi ( ! ) Kuri Gukuramo: i Inyumvo Kuva: Rimwe <acronym> </"
"acronym> . "

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "cddbChoice"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify which Internet <acronym>CD</acronym> Database entry to use. Audio "
"<acronym>CD</acronym>s don't have track names, but the Internet <acronym>CD</"
"acronym> Database is a clever system which uses a special unique identifier "
"generated from the number and length of tracks on each <acronym>CD</acronym> "
"to cross-reference a track listing. Track listings are contributed by the "
"Internet community and made available to all. Occasionally there will be "
"multiple entries. You can specify which one to use."
msgstr ""
"<acronym> </acronym> Icyinjijwe Kuri Koresha . <acronym> </acronym> S "
"Amazina , i <acronym> </acronym> ni A Sisitemu A Bidasanzwe Cyo nyine "
"Ikiranga Kuva: i Umubare na Uburebure Bya ku <acronym> </acronym> Kuri "
"Kwambukiranya - Indango A . ku i na Bihari Kuri Byose . Igikubo Ibyinjijwe . "
"Kugaragaza Rimwe Kuri Koresha . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can submit your own track listings using &kscd;, the &kde; <acronym>CD</"
"acronym> player."
msgstr "Tanga ikoresha &kscd; , i &kde; <acronym> </acronym> . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "By default audiocd tries to pick the best one."
msgstr "Mburabuzi Kuri i Bihebuje Rimwe . "

